# IDE
.vscode/

# Helm chart caches written by `kubectl kustomize --enable-helm` next to a
# kustomization.yaml that uses helmCharts. Re-pulled at render time; never
# committed. (No-vendored-charts rule — see CLAUDE.md.)
**/charts/

# Helm chart caches produced by `helm pull --untar` inside the imperative
# install scripts under infrastructure/kubernetes/installation/automated/.
# The script regenerates these on every run.
infrastructure/kubernetes/installation/automated/add-ons/*/kube-prometheus-stack/
